item.title: Pretty close to 99 Ranged
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

[quote=“Mopman, post:24, topic:285478”][quote author=Full Metalst link=topic=377265.msg2846713#msg2846713 date=1246320809]
I’m 15, and I’m surprised that I haven’t been caught by my friends playing it, I’m way too old…
[/quote]

I’m more surprised that you haven’t suicided under peer pressure yet.

Play what the fuck you want, there is no too old.

I still play mmorpgs and im 21, my wow guild has many people >30 in it.[/quote]
This.

I play RS for a couple of reasons. Like the first time I played WoW was when I borrowed my friend’s copy and account; I got killed by a scorpion or giant spider, or something along those lines, and realised that I couldn’t be fucked when I had no idea how to revive myself.
Call me a n00b, but uno…

For the record, quite a few of the people I play with are aged anywhere from 18 to 25. The majority of the player-base is younger, but that’s a non-issue in my eyes. I think 15 year olds are too young to play golf, and 35+ year olds are too old for tennis; that doesn’t stop them.
